Plot python trade network

Source: R/Plot_python_trade.R
plot_python_trade_network.Rd

Plot python trade network

plot_python_trade_network(Taxon, importer = "NO", min_year = 2009)

Arguments

Taxon

Species name

importer

Country of import (defaults to "NO" - Norway)

min_year

A year filter default is >2009 (so start year is 2010)

Value

Visnetwork graph of origin, export and import of live and derived products of pythons

Examples

plot_python_trade_network(Taxon="Python bivittatus")
